      Kanha's fame extends beyond tourism into global conservation impact:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Project Tiger Model:</strong> Template for tiger conservation globally</li>
      <li><strong>Barasingha Success:</strong> Cited in ungulate conservation programs</li>
