      <li><strong>Training Ground:</strong> Forest officers trained at Kanha</li>
      <li><strong>International Recognition:</strong> UNESCO and WWF partnerships</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Unique Aspects Not Found Elsewhere</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Hard-ground Barasingha:</strong> Exclusively at Kanha — nowhere else in the world</li>
      <li><strong>Meadow Ecosystem:</strong> Well-managed open grasslands within forest</li>
      <li><strong>Jungle Book Link:</strong> Direct cultural connection to classic literature</li>
      <li><strong>Four-Zone System:</strong> Diverse experiences from single base</li>
      <li><strong>Project Tiger Origin:</strong> Among the first reserves, with proven long-term success</li>
    </ul>

    <FAQ faqs={faqs} />

